code: @Override public long extractTimestamp(T element, long previousElementTimestamp) {     // make sure timestamps are monotonously increasing, even when the system clock re-syncs     final long now = Math.max(System.currentTimeMillis(), maxTimestamp).     maxTimestamp = now.     return now. }

@Override public Watermark getCurrentWatermark() {     // make sure timestamps are monotonously increasing, even when the system clock re-syncs     final long now = Math.max(System.currentTimeMillis(), maxTimestamp).     maxTimestamp = now.     return new Watermark(now - 1). }
